      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age in a few areas. The exterior has some noticeable scuffs, a few small dings, and the interior shows typical wear on the driver's seat and carpet. While it runs and drives well, it will eventually need attention for a minor oil seep and some suspension bushings that are starting to creak. It's a solid, honest car for someone looking for affordable transportation without needing it to be perfect.",
