    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been reliably maintained. The exterior is clean and presents well, though it does have some minor surface scratches and a few small door dings expected from regular road use. Inside, the cabin is tidy and the upholstery is in great shape with only light wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it runs smoothly, shifts well, and all major features are fully functional. It\u2019s a solid, dependable car that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
