    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It is in absolutely stunning, mint condition\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've totally babied this car since day one, keeping it spotless and staying on top of every single service. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, but it\u2019s finally time for someone else to get behind the wheel and enjoy the ride. If you\u2019ve been looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 46500.0,
