      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This specimen boasts a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Mechanically flawless, the rod bearing service has been performed preventatively, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure structural rigidity. The suspension remains taut with original bushings in exceptional state, while the exterior retains its factory depth and luster. A true purist\u2019s example with zero deferred maintenance and a clean borescope report.",
