      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that has been preserved in showroom condition. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free from rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather remains supple and uncreased, and the original protective plastics are still present in several areas. This car has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen inclement weather. It comes accompanied by a comprehensive binder containing every service receipt from new, confirming a no-expense-spared maintenance history. Mechanically, it performs exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity to own a pristine, investment-quality example for the most discerning enthusiast.",
